answerText: Chordata [or Chordates][10] This plant phylum now only includes mosses, but used to include liverworts and hornworts as well. Its characteristics include multicellular rhizoids which act as an anchor.

question: Question: All members of this phylum have visceral arches and clefts.  [10] Name this animal phylum to which humans belong, characterized by a notochord and an endostyle.
